```

### 7. Self-Import Error
```gts
// âŒ WRONG - Never import the same field you're defining
import AddressField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/address';

export class AddressField extends FieldDef { // Defining AddressField but importing it too
  // ... this will cause conflicts
}

// âœ… CORRECT - Don't import what you're defining
export class AddressField extends FieldDef {
  // ... define the field without importing it
}

// âœ… CORRECT - To extend a base field, import it with a different name or extend directly
import BaseAddressField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/address';

export class FancyAddressField extends BaseAddressField {
  // ... extend the base field with custom behavior
}
```

### 9. Escaping Placeholder Attributes Only
```hbs
