### 13. SVG URL References Don't Work in Boxel
```hbs
<!-- âŒ WRONG - Boxel cannot route url(#id) references -->
<svg>
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="grad">
      <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#6366f1" />
      <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#8b5cf6" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <rect fill="url(#grad)" />
</svg>

<!-- âœ… CORRECT - Use CSS to style SVG elements -->
